#. Description of the plugin
#: disable-comments.php
msgid "Allows administrators to globally disable comments on their site. Comments can be disabled according to post type. You could bulk delete comments using Tools."
msgstr "Allows administrators to globally disable comments on their site. Comments can be disabled according to post type. You could bulk delete comments using Tools."

